   Micheletto, Marco and Montibeller, Andrea and Orru, Giulia and Ortis,
   Alessandro and Perazzo, Pericle and Puglisi, Giovanni and Salvi, Davide
   and Tubaro, Stefano and Tonti, Claudia Melis and Villari, Massimo and
   Vitulano, Domenico},
